Interface ProtocolHandler


  • public interface ProtocolHandler
    Interface for handing URL requests and responses.
    处理URL请求和响应的接口。
    Since:
    6.11

    • Method Summary

      All Methods  Instance Methods  Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      URLResponse onRequest(URLRequest request)
      This method is invoked for each URL request whose protocol equals to the protocol associated with the current ProtocolHandler instance.
      对于协议等于与当前ProtocolHandler实例关联的协议的每个URL请求，将调用此方法。

    • Method Detail

      • onRequest

        URLResponse onRequest(URLRequest request)
        This method is invoked for each URL request whose protocol equals to the protocol associated with the current ProtocolHandler instance.

        If the method throws an exception, it will be treated as if the method returns null - Chromium engine will handle request.

        对于协议等于与当前ProtocolHandler实例关联的协议的每个URL请求，将调用此方法。如果该方法引发异常，则将其视为该方法返回null － Chromium引擎将处理请求。
        Parameters:
        request - provides information about URL request. -提供有关URL请求的信息。
        Returns:
        URLResponse instance if the request is handled, or null if the given request must be handled by Chromium engine. 例如，如果请求已处理，或者给定的请求必须由Chromium引擎处理。
